<?xml version="1.0"?>
<testsuites tests="9" failed="0">
  <testsuite name="Authorization Failure Reporting"/>
  <testsuite name="Configure SDK to authorize all requests using a specific access token"/>
  <testsuite name="Inspect the access token which the SDK is using to authorize requests"/>
  <testsuite name="Grant an access token">
    <testcase name="Grant an access token with all permissions on all resource types with authorized uuid" steps="66"/>
    <testcase name="Grant an access token without an authorized uuid" steps="9"/>
    <testcase name="Grant an access token successfully with an authorized uuid" steps="10"/>
    <testcase name="Attempt to grant an access token with all permissions empty or false and expect a server error" steps="12"/>
    <testcase name="Attempt to grant an access token with a regular expression containing a syntax error and expect a server error" steps="12"/>
    <testcase name="Attempt to grant an access token with a regular expression containing capturing groups and expect a server error" steps="12"/>
  </testsuite>
  <testsuite name="Parse Access Token">
    <testcase name="Validate that a token containing authorized uuid can be parsed correctly" steps="4"/>
    <testcase name="Validate that a token containing uuid resource permissions can be parsed correctly" steps="5"/>
    <testcase name="Validate that a token containing uuid pattern permissions can be parsed correctly" steps="5"/>
  </testsuite>
  <testsuite name="Revoke an access token"/>
  <testsuite name="provide an access token to the the SDK to authorize requests"/>
  <testsuite name="Message encryption"/>
  <testsuite name="Files"/>
  <testsuite name="History"/>
  <testsuite name="Message Actions"/>
  <testsuite name="Publish a message"/>
  <testsuite name="Signal"/>
  <testsuite name="Push Notifications"/>
  <testsuite name="Subscribing to a channel automatically connects"/>
  <testsuite name="Unsubscribing to all Channels automatically disconnects"/>
  <testsuite name="Check for Messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Maximum allowed reconnection attempt configuration"/>
  <testsuite name="Reconnection policy"/>
  <testsuite name="Continuously receive messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Subscribe Loop auto-retry with access denied"/>
  <testsuite name="Subscribe Loop"/>
  <testsuite name="De-duplicate messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Detect Missed Messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Can stop receiving messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a file event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a message action added event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a message action event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a message event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a channel metadata deleted event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a channel metadata set event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a membership added event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a membership removed event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a user metadata deleted event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a user metadata set event"/>
  <testsuite name="Presence events"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a join event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a leave event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a state change event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a timeout event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a signsal event"/>
  <testsuite name="Receiving a status event"/>
  <testsuite name="Limit unsuccessful reconnection attempts"/>
  <testsuite name="Can trigger the SDK to receive messages"/>
  <testsuite name="Exponential Reconnection Policy"/>
  <testsuite name="Linear Reconnection Policy"/>
  <testsuite name="Restore Serialized Connection State"/>
  <testsuite name="Serialize Connection State"/>
  <testsuite name="Get Connection Status"/>
  <testsuite name="Inspect the number of subsequent failed reconnection attempts"/>
  <testsuite name="Inspect automatic reconnection delay"/>
  <testsuite name="Get Subscribed Channel Groups"/>
